robert alan morse ( born may 18 , 1931 ) is an american actor and singer best known as the star of both the 1961 original broadway production and 1967 movie version of how to succeed in business without really trying , and as bertram cooper , from 2007 to 2015 , in the amc dramatic series mad men .

1960s broadway : this musical with robert morse opened october 14 , 1961 & closed in 1965 after 1,415 performances

